ense at any time for any reason.","termsUseLi4":"Though all efforts have been made to ensure the accuracy of the content on Parichay, the same should not be construed as a statement of law or used for any legal purposes. In case of any ambiguity or doubts, users are advised to verify/check with the concerned Ministry/Department/Organization and/or other source(s), and to obtain appropriate professional advice.","termsUseLi5":"Under no circumstances will the Government Ministry/Department/Organization be liable for any expense, loss or damage including, without limitation, indirect or consequential loss or damage, or any expense, loss or damage whatsoever arising from use, or loss of use, of data, arising out of or in connection with the use of Parichay.","termsUseLi6":"The service offered by Parichay is for your personal use only and not for commercial exploitation. You may not decompile, reverse engineer, disassemble, rent, lease, loan, sell, sublicense, or create derivative works from Parichay. Nor may you use any network monitoring or discovery software to determine the Application/site architecture, or extract information about usage, individual identities or users. You will not use any robot, spider, other automatic software or device, or manual process to monitor or copy Parichay and its contents without NIC\'s prior written permission. You will not copy, modify, reproduce, republish, distribute, display, or transmit for commercial, non-profit or public purposes all or any portion of Parichay, except to the extent permitted by the copyright policy of this terms of use. Any unauthorized use of Parichay.","userResponsibility":"USER RESPONSIBILITY","userResponsibilityText":"As a responsible user, you must:","userResponsibilityLi1":"Be a natural person to access or seek to access Service.","userResponsibilityLi2":"Parichay Service account.","userResponsibilityLi3":"Details on Parichay may only be accessed through the Parichay portal, and only using the username and authentication details which have been specifically allocated to you.","userResponsibilityLi4":"You must not transmit via Parichay any unlawful, defamatory, obscene, offensive or scandalous material, or any material that constitutes or encourages conduct that would contravene any law.","userResponsibilityLi5":"If, within your Parichay account, you are asked to provide information, the information you supply must be complete and accurate. You acknowledge that if you supply incomplete, inaccurate or false information, use Parichay to perform (or attempt to perform) an unauthorized action, or otherwise misuse Parichay then it may suspend or terminate your Parichay access.","userResponsibilityLi6":"Giving false or misleading information is a serious offence. Providing incomplete, inaccurate or false information via Parichay will be treated in the same way as providing incorrect information on a form or in person and may result in prosecution and civil or criminal penalties.","userResponsibilityText2":"Material featured on this website/portal shall not be reproduced anywhere without the explicit written permission of NIC. However, if the material has to be reproduced with permission, then such reproduction should be done accurately and not to be used in a derogatory manner or in a misleading context. Wherever the material is being published or issued to others, the source must be prominently acknowledged. However, the permission to reproduce this material shall not extend to any material which is identified as being copyright of a third party (user submitted content). Authorization to reproduce such material must be obtained from the copyright holder concerned.","Hyperlink":"HYPERLINKING POLICY","hyperLinkPSub1":"Links to external websites/portals","hyperLinkPSub2":"Links to Parichay by other websites/portals","HyperlinkTextLink":"Links to external websites/portals","HyperlinkText":"At some places on Parichay, you shall find links to other websites/portals. These links