e Service :","skipButton":"Continue","skipButtons":"Go to Parichay Home","help_img":"images/help_menu_en.png","submit_img":"url(images/next-button-en.png) no-repeat; height: 40px!important; width: 90px; border: 0!important;","attempts_exceed_msg":"Your Credentials Attempt Exceeded! Please try again","txtBackupCode":"Enter Backup Code","lang_name":"English","redirecting_to_service":"Redirecting to service","successfully_logged_in":"Successfully logged in to Parichay","access_file_page":"ACCESS TO FILE/PAGE WAS DENIED","p_this_Service_content":"You are not authorized to access this service.","p_content_please_contact":"Please contact with Service Coordinator","salient_features_p1":"Salient features","salient_features_li1":"Provides e-Authentication as a service to government departments for providing a secure and convenient way for users to access government services as well as for the government departments to assess the authenticity of the users.","salient_features_li2":"Designed to formulate authentication standards and develop pluggable authentication components for seamless user onboarding and authentication.","salient_features_li3":"Authenticates the user for all the services and does authorization based on the service enforced verification parameters.","salient_features_li4":"Integrated with multiple backend verification parameters including Aadhaar Card, Pan Card, Driving License, Application dependent Id and others.","salient_features_li5":"Allows user as well as integrated service to enforce multi-factor authentication including OTP, Backup Codes, Tap and Token.","salient_features_li6":"Offers Real-time analytics capabilities via Parichay Analytics application, which help to identify a user session activity thus reducing potential profile hacks.","salient_features_li7":"Extended to any number of user bases but restricted to the size of the backend infrastructure cluster.","about_us_p1":"Parichay is a single sign-on application designed to integrate services under a single authentication domain. It is a centralized session and user authentication service in which one set of login credentials can be used to access multiple applications. The service authenticates user one on one designated platform, enabling the user to use a plethora of services without having to log in and logout each time.","about_us_p2":"The sole purpose of the application is to provide SSO framework for the various Government services along with an added layer of security by providing a strong authentication mechanism.","invalid_service_p1":"The requested service name is invalid or the service is not yet registered!","invalid_logout_p1":"Failed to logout!","invalid_logout_p2":"Invalid Service Parameters","single_login_p1":"Access Denied!","single_login_p2":"At a time, only Single Login Allowed","backToLoginBtn":"Back to Login","forgot_pass":"Forgot Password","goToParichay":"Go To Parichay","close_btn":"Close","ok":"Ok","redirected_pass_app":"You will now be Redirected to \'PASS APP\'","redirected_reg_comp":"You will now be Redirected to \'Register Complaint\'","serviceTimeout":"Service Timeout","update_mobile":"Update Mobile Number","btn":"test","invalid_hmac_p1":"Data Integrity Lost","go_to_parichay_login":"Go to Parichay","go_to_client":"Go to Client Service","invalid_encr_p1":"Data Confidentiality Lost","confirmText":"You will now be Redirected to \'NIC Service Desk Portal\'","facing_issue":"Facing issue in accessing Service","backup_code_disable_text":"Please enable Backup Code Setting to use this option","updateProfile":"You will now be Redirected to \'eForms Update Profile Portal\'","sslIssue":"Facing Parichay certificate expiry issue, Update your OS and Browser. For more detail","PrivacyPolicy":"Privacy Policy","privacy_policy_p1":"This website does not automatically capture any specific personal information about you (like name, phone number or e-mail address), that allows us to identify you individually. The website verifies username and password by connecting with a directory service that uses the LDAP protocol and none of your data is stored by the website.Wherever the Website requests you to provide personal information, you will be informed for the particular purposes for which the information is gathered and adequate security measures will be taken to protect your personal information. This website records your activities and logs the information for statistical purposes which includes your IP address, domain name, browser type, operating system, the date and time you access the site, the pages you have accessed, and the previously used devices. We will not identify users or their browsing activities, except when a law enforcement agency may exercise a warrant to inspect the service provider\'s logs. Your email address will only be recorded if you choose to send a message. It will only be used for the purpose for which you have provided it and will not be added to a mailing list. Your email address will not be used for any other purpose, and will not be disclosed, without your consent. If you are asked for any other Personal Information you will be informed about how it will be used. Any information provided to this Website will be protected from loss, misuse, unauthorized access or disclosure, alteration, or destruction. A cookie is a piece of software code that an internet web site sends to your browser when you access information at the site. This website uses cookies. If at any time you believe the principles referred in this privacy statement have not been followed, or have any other comments on these principles, please notify the concerned through the contact us page.","privacy_policy_p2":"","privacy_policy_p3":"Hyperlink Policy","privacy_policy_p4":"","privacy_policy_p5":"","privacy_policy_p6":"","chkDontAskMe_tooltip_text":"Device is being identified by Device IP, User Agent, Browser and OS.\\nIf any of the parameter changes, the device get changed, thus multifactor authentication will be asked again.","linksToExternal":"Links to external websites/portals","linksToExternal_text":"At many places in this Portal, you shall find links to other websites/portals. These links have been placed for your convenience. NIC is not responsible for the content and reliability of the linked websites and does not necessarily endorse the views expressed in them. The mere presence of the link or its listing on this Portal should not be assumed as endorsement of any kind. We cannot guarantee that these links will work all the time and we have no control over availability of linked pages.","linksToJanParichay":"Links to Parichay by other websites","linksToParichay_text":"We do not object to you linking directly to the information that is hosted on this Portal and no prior permission is required for the same. However, we would like you to inform us about any links provided to this Portal so that you can be informed of any changes therein. Also, we do not permit our pages to be loaded into frames on your site. The pages belonging to this Portal must load into a newly opened browser window of the User.","AppPrivacyPolicy":"Parichay Authenticator Privacy Policy","privacy_policy_a1":"Wherever the Parichay Authenticator requests you to provide personal information, you will be informed of the particular purposes for which the information is gathered and adequate security measures will be taken to protect your personal information. We are committed to protect the security of this information and safeguard your privacy. This privacy policy sets out the details of the personal information collected, how it is collected, by whom as well as the purposes for which it is used. At registeration you accepted the terms of this Privacy Policy and your use of the App signifies your continued acceptance thereof. This Privacy Policy may be revised from time to time and you will be notified of all such changes.To use the App, you will be required to consent to the terms of the Privacy Policy as revised from time to time.","access_need":"What accesses do we need?","app_para":"Parichay Authenticator is a mobile app that uses certain features of your device for ensuring your user registeration/enrolment. When you register on the App, the following information is collected from you and stored securely on a server operated and managed by the Government of India (Server). This information will be stored on the Server and a unique Digital Id (DID) will be pushed to your App. The DID will thereafter be used to identify you in all subsequent App related transactions and will be associated with any data or information uploaded from the App to the Server","app_option_1":"Device\'s name to complete your registeration and bind your device.","app_option_2":"Camera permission to scan QR code displayed on Parichay Web for Parichay Authenticator Login / Registeration","security_h1":"Security","security_para1":"Parichay Authenticator is a security app and ensures that none of your data is shared with anyone. We follow generally accepted industry standards to protect any once we receive it The App is equipped with standard security features to protect the confidentiality and security of your information. Data is encrypted in transit as well as at rest. Personal information provided at the time of registeration is encrypted before being uploaded to the government cloud where it is stored in a secure encrypted server.","grievances":"Grievances","kht":"Kavach Hard token","support_1":"If you have any concerns or questions about this Privacy Policy, you may address them to support[hyphen]parichay[at]nic[dot]in","requires_1":"Parichay Authenticator requires","device_details":"Device Details","seemlessSecure":"Seamless & secure","authToAccess":"Authentication to access Parichay and Integrated Applications","seemlessContent":"The application enables you to access Parichay and various other government applications integrated with Parichay through a seamless 2-step verification process. Parichay Authenticator offers both token verification and tap verification for the authentication and authorization of the users.","scanQrCode":"Scan this QR Code to download Parichay Authentication App.","know_more":"Know More","click_here":"Click Here","instructions":"for more details.","downloadAuthenticator":"Download Parichay Authenticator Mobile App for Seamless and Secure Multi Factor Authentication","parichay_auth":"Parichay Authenticator","seemlessSecureMultiFactor":"( Seamless Secure Multi-factor Authentication )","appEnables":"The application enables you to access the various government applications through a seamless 2-step verification process. Parichay Authenticator offers both token verification and tap verification for the authentication and authorization of the users.","authAboutContent":"Parichay Authenticator is a comprehensive, reliable, and secure framework that offers a variety of multifactor authentication solutions like Token Authentication and Tap Authentication to various integrate services including Parichay, Jan Parichay, VPN, and others. It also helps in securing the device by providing local device authentication parameters which includes Pattern, Pin, and Fingerprint.","functionality":"Functionality","functionalityContent":"The application authenticates you through a two-step authentication process where a user needs to provide a secondary factor of authentication along with the password.","tapAuth":"Tap Authentication","tapAuthContent":"For Tap-based authentication, a user needs to tap a prompt sent by the authenticator to registered client device. The prompt will ask if the user is allowed to access the online application or not. Following are benefits of Tap Authentication.","tapAuthContent1":"Easy, quick and convenient real time authentication solution.","tapAuthContent2":"Authenticates user identity with a single tap.","tapAuthContent3":"Single-tap authentication effectively helps in securing the data in a hassle-free way in addition to meeting the required compliances.","tapAuthContent4":"Access Jan Parichay, and integrated services with a single tap.","tokenAuth":"Token Authentication","tokenAuthContent":"For Token-based authentication, a user needs use a soft token generated every 30 seconds by the online application and client device simultaneously. Following are the benefits of Token Authentication.","tokenAuthList1":"This authentication factor adds a second layer of security to application, network, or service access.","tokenAuthList2":"Provides seamless access to Jan Parichay and integrated services.","stepwise":"Stepwise Guide to enable tap/token authentication on Parichay Authenticator","userManual":"User Manual","toDownload":"to Download the","download":"Download ","Step1":"Step 1:","Step2":"Step 2:","Step3":"Step 3:","Step4":"Step 4:","Step5":"Step 5:","Step6":"Step 6:","Step7":"Step 7:","Step8":"Step 8:","Step9":"Step 9:","Step10":"Step 10:","Step11":"Step 11:","Step12":"Step 12:","Step13":"Step 13:","featuredS":"Featured Services","recentServiceT":"Recently used Services","stepContent1":"Go to parichay.nic.in","stepContent2":"Enter your username and password in the required fields and click on the \u201cNext\u201d button.","stepContent3":"Select either \u201cOTP on Mobile\u201d or \u201cBackup Code\u201d and click on the \u201cNext\u201d button to proceed.","stepContent4":"Enter the \u201cOTP\u201d in the required field and click on \u201cNext\u201d button to complete the two-step verification process.","stepContent5":"Click on the top-right \u201cbutton\u201d to see the \u201cSettings\u201d option.","stepContent6":"Click on the \u201cSettings\u201d option to proceed.","stepContent7":"Click on the \u201cOFF\u201d button to turn \u2018\u2019ON\u2019\u2019 the Multi-factor Authentication in Account Settings tab.","stepContent8":"Now, you have to scan the QR using the Scanner of Parichay Authenticator app on your mobile.","stepContent9":" Open the Parichay Authenticator app on your smartphone. Click on the \u201cSkip\u201d button to proceed.","stepContent10":"Choose any one of the \u201cScreen lock type\u201d ","stepContent11":"Click on the \u201cScan QR Code\u201d Button.","stepContent121":"Scan the QR using your smartphone camera.","stepContent122":"Now, you will be able to see the token, use this to configure your account.","stepContent131":"Enter the six-digit token number in the required field below the QR Code.","stepContent132":"Now, you have successfully configured your account with Parichay Authenticator for multi-factor authentication.","spanUserDetails":"Please enter details to proceed","useAsPrimery":"Do you want to use this ID as your primary account?","spanSelectAcc":"Please select one account to proceed","hTipOfDay":"Tip of the day","hQuoteOfDay":"Quote of the day","privacyPolicy":"Privacy Policy","aMinistryofElectronics":"Ministry of Electronics and \\n Information Technology \\nGovernment of India","backToMFAtxt":"Back to MFA Options","divQRContent1":"Scan this QR Code to download Parichay Authentication App. <a href=\'#\' style=\'text-decoration:underline\'>Click here</a> for more details.","divKavachContent":"Parichay Authenticator should be downloaded only from authentic platforms.","downloadKavachtxt":"Kavach","downloadParichayAuthtxt":"Parichay Authenticator","profileUpdateLink":"Update Mobile & \\n Profile","useKavach":"How to use","invalid_saml_p1":"Invalid SAML request. Either Artifact Id in not valid or SAML request is not properly processed!","extended":"Extend ID \\n(Retired Officers)","access_denied_geofencing":"You are not able to access this service according to applied country policy for GeoFencing.","isAuthT":"This is only AuthId. Do not share it with anyone for receiving Email.","contact_us":"Contact Us","home":{"banner":{"title":"Parichay","desc1":"Single Sign-On Platform","desc2":"For Government of India","desc3":"Single login to access multiple government services from various departments."},"about":{"title":"About Us","desc":"Parichay is an SSO framework designed for the Government to Government (G2G) Services which also provides an added layer of security through a strong authentication mechanism. For government users, it eliminates the need to prove their identity while accessing different applications and for application owners, this intuitive platform saves time, effort, and cost to build the authentication environments for every service independently. The platform is an extensive enhancement towards cyber security as it holds different credentials for each user and helps in the identification of real applications as opposed to fake ones."},"counter":{"enrolled":"Enrolled Users","integrated":"Integrated Services","transactions":"Transactions"},"Benefits":{"title":"Key Benefits","Multifactor":{"title":"Multifactor Authentication","desc":"By using Parichay Authenticator, users can enable multiple-factor authentication to login Parichay via Tap, and Token Authentication."},"Standard":{"title":"Standard Integration Methods","desc":"Application owners can opt for various integration methods to integrate their application with Parichay i.e. Rest APIs, SAML 2.0, and OAuth 2.0 ."},"RealTime":{"title":"Real-time analytics","desc":"An analytical dashboard to track user activities and reduce suspicious actions."},"Geofencing":{"title":"Geofencing","desc":"Users can restrict their individual access for specific locations by enabling the virtual boundaries."},"Multilingual":{"title":"Multilingual Support","desc":"The platform offers multiple language support to meet the diverse understanding of the users PAN india."}},"vas":{"title":"Value Added Services","Parichay":{"title":"Parichay Authenticator","desc":"Parichay Authenticator enables user to securely access the various services integrated with Parichay via multi-factor authentication i.e tap and token authenication."},"Analytics":{"title":"Analytics","desc":"ML-enabled analytical dashboard that helps in tracking user authentication & session activities using real-time data processing. This comprehensive service in highly effective in Threat detection and Hack mitigation framework."}},"faq":{"title":"Frequently Asked Questions","faq1":{"title":"What is a Single Sign-On Platform?","desc":"Single Sign-On is a centralized session and user authentication service in which a set of login credentials can be used to access multiple applications during the same session. The service helps in providing a seamless user experience by eliminating the need of proving the user identity to different applications."},"faq2":{"title":"What is Parichay?","desc":"Parichay is the Single Sign-On service for Government of India that authenticates government users easily and securely. It provides government users with seamless access to multiple application via two-step multifactor authentication powered by Parichay Authenticator and Kavach."},"faq3":{"title":"What are the key benefits of using Parichay?","desc":"The basic objective of Parichay is to eliminate the individual & repetitive sign-on procedures by centralizing user authentication and identity management at a central identity provider. Its intuitive interface allows better user mobility and provides seamless access to multiple government services by authenticating just once."},"faq4":{"title":"How can I join Parichay?","desc":"Parichay is a Single Sign-on platform for Government of India and a government employee/user may register on Parichay using their Government Ids."},"faq5":{"title":"What is the Login Process for Parichay?","desc":"Parichay follows the two-step multi-factor authentication for user Login process. A government user can login Parichay using their credentials: Government Id/username and password generated at the time of registration. After that, OTP verification is performed and on successful verification the user is redirected to the dashboard."}},"contact":{"title":"Contact Us","address":"National Informatics Centre,Bloc